{"tid":1536820,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經] 被捕需知：李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T16:15:17.000Z","uid":127929,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"931a794393fa5796b815f0ee0f33cbf1a0ea1fd0","tid":1536820,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Too long don't read</span></span><br />\n1. 「我無嘢講」係由你捕嗰刻開始直到律師嚟之前, <span style=\"color: red;\">對乜人 (包括手足/家長)都冇嘢講</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 「我無嘢講」唯一風險係打贏官司冇得拎返律師費<br />\n<br />\n3. 千其唔好解鎖手機/比密碼班狗, <span style=\"color: red;\">用狗屋電話搵家人/律師</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 狗隻<span style=\"color: red;\">除非有你同意/ 搜查令, 否則無權</span>拎你手機密碼/ 上你屋企搜屋<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果被酷刑, 要<span style=\"color: red;\">認住黑警同嗰個地方個樣</span>, 然後請律師搵當值官認人+跟進<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKanZhongGuo.web%2Fvideos%2F486314495263561%2F%3Fv%3D486314495263561&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=41b8432d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧己及人，就算唔睇原post都要<span style=\"color: red;\">推比未睇既人睇</span><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」 (文字版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512130</a>"},{"pid":"e18182965576fab5a59a7bb705a57c9eb39bf411","tid":1536820,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"我每個post 都會咒一次：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) <br />\n908 九月八日 2:00pm <